{"tid":2287341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃大仙嗇色園登報祝賀陳百祥獲授銅紫荊星章 封號為「吾知道長」","createTime":"2020-11-15T16:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T02:25:19.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3618212d513bf597bceda2203fe1227118eb1f09","tid":2287341,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TTwMi9nfcv1BRonjnSaZhexUv8U=/802x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QJ2KLRM6PFHNFBG6P54IQ4RPXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTTwMi9nfcv1BRonjnSaZhexUv8U%3D%2F802x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQJ2KLRM6PFHNFBG6P54IQ4RPXE.jpg&h=54f853ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一向以「唔知」、「睇唔到」、「我唔信」撐警的陳百祥（阿叻）獲授銅紫荊星章。去得禮賓府受勳，阿叻當然要着得得體啲，今日佢就以一套黑色軍閥feel套裝現身，不過卻被眼利嘅網民發現，原來淘寶都有類似嘅衫賣，而且只係賣248人仔（約291港幣），勁抵玩！<br />\n<br />\n另外，阿叻係今年唯一一個娛樂圈嘅人獲得勳章，當然要大肆慶祝一下，黃大仙嗇色園就登報祝賀，不過唔講唔知，原來身為資深會員嘅阿叻有個朵叫「吾知道長」，連個朵都叫「吾知」，難怪佢之前同杜汶澤上港台節目《視點31》時，對有關反送中運動處於「我唔知」、「我睇唔到」、「我唔識」狀態。<br />\n<br />\n據資料顯示，其實阿叻做「吾知道長」前，要先修讀道教文化班同通過面試，更要接受一連串考核，先至可以升格做道長，而道長亦有義務推廣黃大仙信仰文化，以及協助處理嗇色園事務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201114/OI4ZOVW62BERNM7ENCWFNCGVAI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201114%2FOI4ZOVW62BERNM7ENCWFNCGVAI%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3tagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b860d683\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201114%2FOI4ZOVW62BERNM7ENCWFNCGVAI%2F&h=ac2b08db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201114/OI4ZOVW62BERNM7ENCWFNCGVAI/</a>"},{"pid":"f2e616f73efa04656029bb66a69ec3a754f6bfcf","tid":2287341,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\